Head. Antennae nearly as long as head. Ant. IV with a subapical organite and basolateral ms about 1 / 4 of segment length from base. Ant. III sensory organ composed of 5 papillae, 5 guard chaetae, 2 small sensory rods, 2 granulated sensory clubs and a lateral ms (
Figs 2 & 3
