Appendages. Subcoxa 1 of legs I–III with 5, 7 and 6–7 chaetae, subcoxa 2 with 1, 5 and 5 chaetae, respectively. Tibiotarsi of legs I–III with 22 ( 11, 8 , 3 ), 21 ( 11, 8 , 2 ) and 22–23 ( 11, 8 , 3 or 4 ) chaetae, respectively. Unguis with small inner denticle. Unguiculus slender and pointed, as long as inner edge of unguis, without inner basal lamella (
